{"tid":2008430,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"分佈不均無法殺病毒  免費罩銅粒易入肺損器官","createTime":"2020-05-09T04:41:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T11:58:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":223,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":99,"replies":[{"pid":"2a59648d2b60dd2b79190032a7cf98de8c4b67e7","tid":2008430,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:41:29.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200509/O2S37RTXPRQUGLMQFE5IPGD2BM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200509%2FO2S37RTXPRQUGLMQFE5IPGD2BM%2F&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d3XW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=712797ab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200509%2FO2S37RTXPRQUGLMQFE5IPGD2BM%2F&h=77d7f30d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200509/O2S37RTXPRQUGLMQFE5IPGD2BM/</a><br />\n<br />\n分佈不均無法殺病毒 <br />\n免費罩銅粒易入肺損器官<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【肺炎大爆發】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】豪花納稅人八億元的「銅芯抗疫口罩」（Cu Mask），缺失就像口罩內層，越揭越有。有專研納米粒子及過濾技術的權威學者分析，Cu Mask有四大問題，包括標榜具抗菌抗病毒功能的銅分佈不均，無法捕捉及殺滅病毒、納米銅體積太小，容易穿吸入肺、口罩過濾層太厚難以透氣，以及未能通過歐洲一級標準。<br />\n<br />\n記者：伍雅謙<br />\n<br />\nHKRITA行政總裁葛儀文（左）昨在記招上展示銅芯口罩內層。馬泉崇攝<br />\n<br />\n創科局及HKRITA多番強調銅芯口罩含銅，。。。。。。。。<br />\n含有銅粒子。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：創科局辯稱專利改良版<br />\n<br />\n「擺咗小型炸彈喺度」<br />\n<br />\n研發口罩多年的理大機械工程學系創新產品與科技講座教授梁煥方表示，銅可黏實病毒，有殺滅病毒及細菌功能，並非新科技，但首要是能捕捉到病毒才能殺滅。惟他指出，從口罩第一層的深色紗線分佈可見只有約20%至30%銅，未能完全覆蓋口罩，紗線直徑亦較大，不利於捕捉病毒。以顯微鏡觀察口罩第三層，物料密度並不高，病毒可輕易穿透，當中的銅粒子分佈不平均，未必能捕捉到病毒，「接觸唔到點殺到箒」，直斥口罩的銅分佈不均，令消毒功能無效。<br />\n<br />\n口罩含銅會否影響健康一直受關注。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n口罩貼近口鼻，納米銅容易被吸入肺部，再經肺部微絲血管，透過血液將重金屬銅粒子帶至各器官，形容Cu Mask是「擺咗啲小型炸彈喺度」。。。。。。。。口罩第四層的過濾層亦未能完全隔離0.1微米或小於0.1微米的銅粒子。他提醒，反覆洗滌Cu Mask致使用者吸入納米銅，或引起嚴重慢性健康問題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200509/large/1588955394_4d49.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200509%2Flarge%2F1588955394_4d49.gif&h=07a3452e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n洗得多纖維走樣影響透氣<br />\n<br />\nCu Mask第四層。。。。。。。。<br />\n卻犧牲透氣度。。。。。。。。。透氣度的壓降（differential pressure），口罩清洗前數值平均有4.44，清洗40次後是4.82，其中一個超過5，不符合美國ASTM一級標準。他提醒，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\nCu Mask早前標榜通過美國ASTM一級標準，今日HKRITA行政總裁葛儀文教授。。。。。。。。。公佈的報告顯示不達標。梁煥方指出，此口罩壓降數值達4.44，並不適合長者、患者及有呼吸系統問題的人士佩戴。"},{"pid":"1b02bdc1a02e0f41f7f82e9758c0f0e5059e873b","tid":2008430,"uid":36901,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:42:40.000Z","msg":"好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8351d70dd15abfbb6ef67be4f969b9ccdf1e5d36","tid":2008430,"uid":46910,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:42:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />政府冇好野"},{"pid":"ba69f6a05d5bf76c986903af480a3d5b5eb1bebc","tid":2008430,"uid":97080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:43:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c0538d08dbadcba252f9c9441ee6ea11bca61ac","tid":2008430,"uid":357636,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:44:28.000Z","msg":"洗左幾錢話？呢個防菌，呀唔係，蒙面口罩"},{"pid":"cc5a3f72c33db3ffffdb2f561d109dd2b4fdc11d","tid":2008430,"uid":171192,"like":65,"dislike":0,"score":65,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:48:58.000Z","msg":"創科局聲稱&ldquo;納米&rdquo;銅先需要擔心，可重用口罩濾芯只係&ldquo;微粒&rdquo;銅&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n痴撚線話用銅隔/殺菌<br />\n結果將金屬微粒吸哂入肺度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未畀隻肺炎整壞個肺已經畀啲金屬微粒搞壞咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌那星以後貼住塊面嘅嘢同啲噴霧查哂成分先敢用<br />\n隻19口罩藍絲小粉紅要用你地用飽去<br />\n我俾埋我嗰份你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5044c57db0fe0c7bfb6947c34135f32b18f7e9f8","tid":2008430,"uid":20563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:50:03.000Z","msg":"真係戴左就bye 9 bye"},{"pid":"e3162659140652771854314183c39d972658cc6d","tid":2008430,"uid":270438,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"2c0538d08dbadcba252f9c9441ee6ea11bca61ac","tid":2008430,"uid":357636,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:44:28.000Z","msg":"洗左幾錢話？呢個防菌，呀唔係，蒙面口罩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:51:26.000Z","msg":"推蒙面法 但派蒙面口罩"},{"pid":"88d9ed8ec999bb4f89cc40c29f0b43e49798a537","tid":2008430,"uid":29423,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:51:27.000Z","msg":"成件事好中國特色 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22019bdbc74d42da3f64afe02ea47a4702e1e4fe","tid":2008430,"uid":50740,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:52:50.000Z","msg":"藍屍死晒冇鐵票唷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff519d11e06384debe2344edb7c6202008d6032a","tid":2008430,"uid":7760,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:53:31.000Z","msg":"用政府提供既口罩去抗爭遮樣就可以留啲外科口罩平時用"},{"pid":"dceaf97d43a6cd96322cee8c3e2b972be45a01b9","tid":2008430,"uid":7760,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ff519d11e06384debe2344edb7c6202008d6032a","tid":2008430,"uid":7760,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:53:31.000Z","msg":"用政府提供既口罩去抗爭遮樣就可以留啲外科口罩平時用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:54:01.000Z","msg":"補充： 唔用個濾芯"},{"pid":"f5a6d7c2b683c527029d6eddad5721a0b140288d","tid":2008430,"uid":64743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime